'''林賢洙'''（{{lang-ko|임현수}}，{{bd|1955年|2月16日||}}）是一名韓裔[[加拿大|加拿大]]牧師<ref name="ctvnews1">{{cite web |url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/world/north-korea-sentences-canadian-to-life-in-prison-for-anti-state-activities-1.2702243 |title=North Korea sentences Canadian to life in prison for 'anti-state activities' | CTV News |website=Ctvnews.ca |date=2014-05-08 |access-date=2015-12-16 |publisher=[[CTV_News|CTV News]] |archive-date=2021-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111091916/https://www.ctvnews.ca/world/north-korea-sentences-canadian-to-life-in-prison-for-anti-state-activities-1.2702243 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，任職於[[密西沙加|密西沙加]]大光教會（{{lang-ko|큰빛교회}}）。他曾在[[朝鮮|朝鮮]]進行[[人道主義|人道主義]]工作，為其提供了价值数千万美元的援助<ref name="theglobeandmail1">{{cite news |author=Canada |url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/unravelling-the-mystery-behind-the-detention-of-reverend-lim/article24481630/ |title=Unravelling the mystery behind the detention of reverend Lim |publisher=[[The_Globe_and_Mail|The Globe and Mail]] |access-date=2015-12-16 |archive-date=2020-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812065645/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/unravelling-the-mystery-behind-the-detention-of-reverend-lim/article24481630/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，直至2015年2月失踪<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.thestar.com/news/gta/2015/03/05/gta-pastor-confirmed-held-in-north-korea.html |title=GTA pastor confirmed held in North Korea |website=Thestar.com |date=2015-03-05 |access-date=2015-12-16 |publisher=[[Toronto_Star|Toronto Star]] |archive-date=2021-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109004301/https://www.thestar.com/news/gta/2015/03/05/gta-pastor-confirmed-held-in-north-korea.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年12月，他被控危害朝鮮政權，判處无期劳动教化刑<ref>{{cite web |last=Shortell |first=Dave |url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/12/16/world/hyeon-soo-lim-canadian-pastor-north-korea-sentence/index.html |title=Hyeon Soo Lim gets life sentence in North Korea |website=CNN.com |access-date=2015-12-16 |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110115537/https://www.cnn.com/2015/12/16/world/hyeon-soo-lim-canadian-pastor-north-korea-sentence/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2017年8月，加拿大總理[[贾斯汀·特魯多|贾斯汀·特魯多]]派出加拿大國際政府代表團前往[[平壤|平壤]]討論此案<ref name="govcapresser">{{cite press release| url=http://pm.gc.ca/eng/news/2017/08/10/statement-prime-minister-canada-pastor-lims-release| title=Statement by the Prime Minister of Canada on Pastor Lim's release| date=August 10, 2017| publisher=[[Government_of_Canada|Government of Canada]]| access-date=2021-01-06| archive-date=2019-07-23| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190723114847/https://pm.gc.ca/eng/news/2017/08/10/statement-prime-minister-canada-pastor-lims-release| dead-url=no}}</ref>。林賢洙於2017年8月9日獲釋<ref name="cbcnews1">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/canadian-pastor-released-1.4239910 |title=North Korea releases imprisoned Canadian pastor - World - CBC News |website=Cbc.ca |access-date=2017-08-09 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112013939/https://www.cbc.ca/news/world/canadian-pastor-released-1.4239910 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並於2017年8月12日回到加拿大<ref name="incanada">{{cite news| url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-northkorea-canada-idUSKBN1AS0Q0| title=Canadian pastor returns home after release from North Korean prison| first=Jim| last=Finkle| publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]| accessdate=2021-01-06| archive-date=2021-01-07| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107200703/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-northkorea-canada-idUSKBN1AS0Q0| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在釋放後的採訪中，林賢洙將自己被捕的原因歸咎於他在[[美國|美國]][[基督教|基督教]]會議上的一段演講視頻。他在視頻中表示，朝鮮人應該“相信[[上帝|上帝]]而不是[[金日成|金日成]]，相信[[耶穌|耶穌]]而不是[[金正日|金正日]]”。這段視頻未經他的允許就被發佈在[[互聯網|互聯網]]上，並被朝鮮當局發現。[http://www.bosnewslife.com/37788-canadian-pastor-jailed-in-north-korea-forgives-those-who-caused-prosecution] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bosnewslife.com/37788-canadian-pastor-jailed-in-north-korea-forgives-those-who-caused-prosecution |date=20180926181834 }}

